<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Salutations!</h1>
    <p style="text-align:center;margin:2em 0 2em 0">
			<%= @host.full_name %> has invited you to their event: <%= @event.name%>. <br/>
			Start Date: <%= @event.display_start_time %>.<br/>
			RSVP: <%= @event.display_rsvp_time %>.
		</p>
		<p style="margin-bottom:1em">If you do not have an account with us, please <%= link_to 'create one', new_user_registration_url %> with the following email address: <%= @attendee.email %>.</p><p>If you do decide to create an account using a different email address, notify <%= @host.full_name %> at <%= @host.email %> and inform them which email you would prefer to use.  Otherwise, please <%= link_to 'sign in', root_url %><br /><br/>
    </p>
    <p>Thanks and have a great day!</p>

  </body>
</html>

